            <h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-4">Setting Up Your Reloading Tracker in Arsenal Vault</h1>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-6">Track your components, save your recipes, and log every batch. No more guessing how many primers you have left.</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
                <span><i class="bi bi-calendar3 mr-1"></i> March 28, 2026</span>
